 a Peridot.  He gives you the Xyfl Scale.  Good aligned are KOS to Tektite.</p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="center"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><A HREF="questmessage.asp?Guide=58">Post a Comment</A></font></p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="center"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><A HREF="quests.asp">Browse other quests</A></font></p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="center"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><A HREF="submitquest.asp">Submit a Quest Walkthrough</A></font></p></td></tr></div></center>
       
